PUBLISHED BY AUTHORITY 
ISLAMABAD, WEDNESDAY, MARCH 19, 2014 
PART II 
Statutory Notifications (S.R.0.) 
GOVERNMENT OF PAKISTAN 
REVENUE DIVISION 
(Federal Board of Revenue) 
NOTIFICATION 
Islamabad, the 18th March, 2014 
(CusToms) 
S.R.O. 202 (10/2014.—In exercise of thy powers conferred by section 
219 of the Customs Act, 1969 (IV of 1969), the Federal Board of Revenue is 
pleased to direct that the following further amendment shall be made in the Customs 
Rules, 2001, namely:— 
In the aforesaid Rules, in rule 343, in sub-rule (1), clauses (j) and (k) shall 
be omitted. 
[C.No.5(7)EP/DRD/2012.] 	
DR. KAMAL AZHAR MINHAS, 
Chief (Customs). 
(615)
